2009_April 1 
When Marty McFly (Michael J. Fox) is contacted by his friend Dr.Brown
(Christopher Lloyd) to help him test out his newest invention,A Time
Machine, Marty doesn&#x27;t know what he&#x27;s in for. The two are attacked by
Libyans and Doc Brown is supposedly killed. Marty jumps into the
DeLorean and transports back to the year 1955. After that, everything
turns to chaos. He accidentely screws up his parents first meeting and
gains Biff as an enemy. With time windling down a thread, he starts to
receive help from Doc 1955 and tries to get his parents together before
he fades from existence. One of the greatest sci-fi films of all time.
Back To The Future 10/10
